local_non_stake.descr: Total token in account that is not staked, due to it being a result of a withdrawal aggregation or rewards

aggregation_tracker.descr: information to assist with tracking users contribution since aggregations can be delayed

vesting_tracker.descr: if account is vesting, vesting information is stored here

manager.descr: Address that is able to modify manager settings and register participation keys

manager_algo_share.descr: The share of algo rewards allocated for the manager of the delegation contract

manager_gora_share.descr: The share of gora rewards allocated for the manager of the delegation contract

global_aggregation_round.descr: Keeps track of current aggregation round, aggregation round start (algorand round), Gora timeout

global_most_recent_aggregation.descr: keeps info about the most recently completed aggregation
